This paper deals with distributed target tracking in wireless sensor networks, which involves communication and consensus algorithms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MA (Multiagent Systems), which deals with the interaction of multiple agents and their coordination. The paper also involves wireless communication, which suggests the category cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The use of consensus algorithms and belief propagation suggests the category cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also deals with distributed computing, which suggests the category cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Finally, the paper involves information theory, which suggests the category cs.IT (Information Theory).
